\n 6. Type \"1.5707\" in the \"Pitch field, then hit \"[Enter]\"\r\n\r\nBoth Roll and Pitch have now been reset to 0 :-(\r\n\r\n![link_inspector_reset.gif](data/bitbucket.org/repo/jgXqbo/images/975976266-link_inspector_reset.gif)", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>To reproduce</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Open the Model Editor</li>\n<li>Add a cylinder to the scene</li>\n<li>Double click on the cylinder to open the Link Inspector</li>\n<li>Scroll down to Pose</li>\n<li>Type \"1.5707\" in the \"Roll\" field, then click outside the field</li>\n<li>Type \"1.5707\" in the \"Pitch field, then hit \"[Enter]\"</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Both Roll and Pitch have now been reset to 0 :-(</p>\n<p><img alt=\"link_inspector_reset.gif\" src=\"data/bitbucket.org/repo/jgXqbo/images/975976266-link_inspector_reset.gif\" /></p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": null, "state": "resolved", "version": null, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2017-01-19T21:32:23.973679+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2018-03-06T03:38:27.275225+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 2154}